  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the world of \"Little Adventurer's Treasure Hunt,\" help alien friends who have crash-landed on Earth to find spaceship parts and embark on a fun and lighthearted treasure hunt!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429910/extras/9334d6e577d764de003aa02a555445c6.poster.avif?t=1746859977\" width=650 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429910/extras/9334d6e577d764de003aa02a555445c6.webm?t=1746859977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429910/extras/9334d6e577d764de003aa02a555445c6.mp4?t=1746859977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whimsical hand-drawn art style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meticulously designed and diverse levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assist those in need to earn rewards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Moderate puzzle-solving with carefully crafted Easter eggs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden cats in achievements waiting to be discovered</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PS: Maybe the target is in the most obvious spot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you encounter any bugs, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:101063791@qq.com\">101063791@qq.com</a>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429910/extras/02ca0bb34bd20e8afd317d22857a38d4.avif?t=1746859977\" width=720 height=700 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the world of \"Little Adventurer's Treasure Hunt,\" help alien friends who have crash-landed on Earth to find spaceship parts and embark on a fun and lighthearted treasure hunt!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429910/extras/9334d6e577d764de003aa02a555445c6.poster.avif?t=1746859977\" width=650 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429910/extras/9334d6e577d764de003aa02a555445c6.webm?t=1746859977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429910/extras/9334d6e577d764de003aa02a555445c6.mp4?t=1746859977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whimsical hand-drawn art style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meticulously designed and diverse levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assist those in need to earn rewards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Moderate puzzle-solving with carefully crafted Easter eggs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden cats in achievements waiting to be discovered</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PS: Maybe the target is in the most obvious spot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you encounter any bugs, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:101063791@qq.com\">101063791@qq.com</a>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429910/extras/02ca0bb34bd20e8afd317d22857a38d4.avif?t=1746859977\" width=720 height=700 /></span></p>",
